{"tid":125739,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump係咁簽行政命令 鋼筆就快斷貨","createTime":"2017-02-18T17:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T04:12:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8bac966b00f26bfbf074794929af4bd12df6556","tid":125739,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>川普愛簽行政命令 鋼筆消耗不是普通快</strong><br />\n<br />\n發稿時間：2017/02/18 20:09<br />\n最新更新：2017/02/18 20:21<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20170218/49476510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20170218%2F49476510.jpg&h=064da6fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（<a href=\"http://圖取自白宮推特網頁twitter.com/WhiteHouse）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81twitter.com%2FWhiteHouse%EF%BC%89&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=a9e511e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自白宮推特網頁twitter.com/WhiteHouse）</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社羅德島州普羅維登斯17日電）美國總統川普就職才4星期，他用來簽署行政命令的高仕牌（Cross）客製鋼筆就快用完了。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，4星期前，川普（Donald Trump）在就職時說：「對了，我想我們將需要更多一些這種鋼筆。」他簽署首道行政命令時，將鋼筆作為紀念品送給觀禮的國會議員，並對他們開玩笑說：「政府變得越來越小氣了，對吧？」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>白宮預期最新一批350枝鍍金鋼筆今天以前會到貨</strong>。這些筆15日已從具170年歷史、位於新英格蘭地區的高仕公司寄出，而這家公司已供應所生產名筆給至少7位美國總統。<br />\n<br />\n不過，川普可能是首位一邊揮舞著鋼筆、一邊展示著每個新簽署法案的總統。毫無疑問這是他施政風格的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n高仕筆至少從福特（Gerald Ford）政府開始供應美國總統使用。2013年賣給一間私募股權公司的高仕，一度是羅德島主要企業，<strong>但如今該公司大部分筆都是在中國生產。</strong><br />\n<br />\n高仕仍試著將美國印記放在總統用筆上。<span style=\"color: red;\">高仕筆目前在中國烤漆和刻字</span>，但最後會使用國內外的零件在羅德島組裝。<br />\n<br />\n高仕公司表示，前總統歐巴馬的高仕筆鍍的是鉻，<strong>川普則換成鍍金</strong>，「顯然，川普愛黃金。」<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：中央社周慧盈）1060218<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201702180324-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201702180324-1.aspx&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=3ad0c043\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201702180324-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"50dcc33adde7ed0d3eb2f73331d908edc98359dc","tid":125739,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd700b5bf6671fdc7d840d91b5c9184d212fb33e","tid":125739,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2446450e7e0feafc4d94f9df4b831801e9ae4443","tid":125739,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:33:54.000Z","msg":"🌬🌊：要不是我國製造&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6c1f94359b10a3fc6fb894be49873c09c82302","tid":125739,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"中國成最大贏家"},{"pid":"4ecc878206d51bd862ce8754008b24269a84fa25","tid":125739,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:42:50.000Z","msg":"trump trump we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n350支有排簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1483fa80201ca30fc53d644cacd8a07241c51180","tid":125739,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:13:18.000Z","msg":"高仕筆目前在中國烤漆和刻字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09643e8fa3dcfcfdc994f6e489a7b152d0dd5e2","tid":125739,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:31:27.000Z","msg":"條友寫字咁大力，簽完一次支筆都拉柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e142ccd2673532b1118825f77c81962caee7a3","tid":125739,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"高士係c